title: Quiz 3 - Syllogism
instruction: Directions (21-25) Study the following information carefully and answer the questions given below. It has been given that- A + B states that All A are B A @ B states that Some A are not B A # B states that No A is B A % B states that Only A is B A & B states that few A is B A *+B states that All A are B is a possibility. A * B states that there is a possibility A=B states that All A can never be B.
